ARM: stop *MIGHT_HAVE_PCI* config from being selected redundantly

*MIGHT_HAVE_PCI* config is already selected in ARCH_MULTIPLATFORM.
Don't select it redundantly in all ARCH_MULTIPLATFORM based machines.

